> can you explain it detaily.


this source code:
```
   /**
     * Load balance strategy, legal values include: random, roundrobin, leastactive
     */
    String loadbalance() default DEFAULT_LOADBALANCE;
```
when we use,we do this:
`@DubboService(loadbalance = "roundrobin")`

better, strategies can be designed as constant, for exemple:
```
public class LoadbalanceStrategy {
    public final static String ROUNDROBIN = "roundrobin";
}

@DubboService(loadbalance = LoadbalanceStrategy.ROUNDROBIN)
```
Similarly，cluster can also be designed like this。this can prevent users from writing mistakes.

