you can use parameter to set the serialization type in consumer side.

like this: 

HashMap<String, String> parameter = new HashMap<>();
parameter.put("serialization", "kryo");
referenceConfig.setParameters(parameter);

> The above solution does not solve the problem of user-defined id. It may be more reliable and simpler to check triples (group, interface, version) before export service.

